* The user who installed the gem package be able to create own plugins.

  * ~/.automatic/plugins

* Utils merged to automatic-config command and added following subcommand.

  * scaffold
  * autodiscovery
  * opmlparser
  * feedparser
  * log

* Added Integration Test Script for CI.

  * script/build


